On the anniversary of the assassination of former Lebanese Prime Minister Rafiq Hariri, the United States reaffirms its support for the Special Tribunal for Lebanon in finding the truth behind the act of terrorism. The US believes that ending the era of impunity for political assassinations is crucial for justice and stability in Lebanon. Any attempt to interfere with the Tribunal's work or fuel tensions in Lebanon should not be tolerated. The US remains committed to supporting the sovereignty, integrity, and independence of Lebanon, as well as the implementation of UN Security Council Resolutions. The US calls on all friends of Lebanon to support the Lebanese people in determining their own destiny and encourages peace and reconciliation in the country.